Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the sweetfish river running through my beloved hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,You who seek the Golden Land, follow its path downstream in search of the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:13.50,Yellow,,0,0,0,,As you travel down it, you will see a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:17.30,Yellow,,0,0,0,,In that village, look for the shore the two will tell you of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.30,Yellow,,0,0,0,,There sleeps the key to the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:24.10,Yellow,,0,0,0,,The one who obtains the key must then travel to the Golden Land in accordance with these rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:31.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the first twilight, offer the six chosen by the key as sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:35.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the second twilight, those who remain shall tear apart the two who are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the third twilight, those who remain shall praise my noble name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the fourth twilight, gouge the head and kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.10,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the fifth twilight, gouge the chest and kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:46.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the sixth twilight, gouge the stomach and kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the seventh twilight, gouge the knee and kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.30,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the eighth twilight, gouge the leg and kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.70,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the ninth twilight, the witch shall revive, and none shall be left alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:01.50,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On the tenth twilight, at journey's end, you shall attain to the power of the Golden Land's treasures, once and for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:05.70,Yellow,,0,0,0,,The witch shall praise the wise and bestow four treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,One,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.30,Yellow,,0,0,0,,shall be all the gold from the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.30,Yellow,,0,0,0,,One,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.70,Yellow,,0,0,0,,shall be the resurrection of all the dead souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,One,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,shall be the resurrection of the love that was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.30,Yellow,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.70,Yellow,,0,0,0,,...shall be to put the witch to sleep for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.70,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sleep peacefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.90,Yellow,,0,0,0,,my beloved witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, George-sama! They're so cute, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute. Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're really cute. I almost want to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I'd feel so sorry for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? But that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's so awesome. It's such a big tank! It's like they sliced off a part of the sea and brought it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting description. A slice of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, this may not be the real sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as long as they swim here and they believe that this is the sea, then to them it certainly is the beautiful sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I feel so happy, it makes me scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect this to happen either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought of how nice it would be if it turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the power of thought is imbued with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think that's magic for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time we meet, you keep becoming more and more beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have grown to be that much more important to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If the same thing happened to you, then the fact that we are here today is simply an inevitable consequence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not some magic or miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,George-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I have one more whim, but I'm not sure if you'd be willing to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, George-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop calling me "George-sama"? At least when it's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's create that as a rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. ...George-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds wonderful. I'm so happy, Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the name Sayo as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, I'll call you Sayo from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Sayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly is a deep blue sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see this sea with you, Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, George-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This sea and the sky are all so blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you can look at it with two people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then it really is real magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With this mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and taste the fruits of that wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this is the only thing I can do when I am trapped on Rokkenjima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Free me from life as furniture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll accept new sufferings, and become human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Break the eternally unchangeable fate that imprisons me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,into pieces!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept my promise, now it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to fulfill my wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama!!
