Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:23.44,JPSong,,0,0,0,,Impossibile arrivare
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to arrive
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:29.97,JPSong,,0,0,0,,Al vero segreto se non ci
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At the truth of the secret if
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:36.39,JPSong,,0,0,0,,Si accorge di tutto l’amore
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One fails to realize all the love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Ushiromiya Eva, Hideyoshi and George are coming to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not neglect your duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I was a middle school student, and sometimes I dreamt of love like children my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, I should not dream like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I am furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoh, that does sound promising. Study a lot at your father's, and do your best to become able to help him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not language or math you learn in school. What you study is the attitude to have towards studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, dear. George is always giving it his all. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly excellent. I wish our Jessica would learn from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ughhh. Are you still holding a grudge about that test score？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica, shouldn't you learn to be a bit more gracious with your speech, not to speak of your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, I will speak to you at length about your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If the little child here is bothering you, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah- Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon, the tea is getting cold. Serve it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I ruined the peaceful atmosphere here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is pounding, I can't afford to make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This tea smells good. Is it Earl Grey tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoh, George-kun, you know a lot about black tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who helped me once explained to me that there used to be an Earl of Grey in England, and this tea was named after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With that knowledge, the tea seems to get taster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it not? Shannon, thank you for the delicious black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,George nii-san could always easily change the topic at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think back on it, I feel that maybe this wasn't the first time he has helped me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really good at reading between the lines in those kinds of situations. That guy's a show-off in weird ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Th, that's not true... I think he is a really wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmmm? Shannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you haven't fallen in love with George nii-san, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys having so much fun talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather finally came down. Now they're having an adult discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaping then was the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather must think of us as the angel of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is not a family meeting - it is a meeting to borrow money for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My family's pretty stingy, why don't they just lend out the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...But, I really wish I could watch from the corner and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, the flowers in this garden are truly splendid this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the atmosphere has changed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... George-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your concern back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember doing anything I should be thanked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart can't stop beating...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, George nii-san, shouldn't you have a girlfriend by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- what is this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you're pretty good at academics, I guess you don't understand at all in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! If George nii-san is up to it, why not practice going on a date with Shannon for a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Th- th- that's a very appealing plan, but... I'd feel bad for Shannon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It- it's okay, I'm j-j-just a servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You both reacted so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,George.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sor...sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude of me, Eva-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father and the rest have finished talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to talk to Grandfather about you, so come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a marriage meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't marriage meetings be done at a more mature age...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we have no desire to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage isn't something you do after you start liking someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about getting married and then getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only son I'm proud of. We'll introduce you to someone who is a fitting partner for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's go. We're keeping Father waiting. Hurry to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you two. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Auntie will leave too. I'm so sorry I interrupted your pleasant conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-chan, I'm sure you'll meet a wonderful person suitable for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, you too, Shannon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you really forgotten to be grateful for your schooling? Know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,George may be the one who will bear the burden of the Ushiromiya family someday in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think you could snatch George away, you uneducated, incompetent, unqualified, uncultured servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! You can definitely find someone who matches you as a servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had forgotten. I am furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be grateful for even being treated like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot ask for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The head and my husband will return very soon. Has the study and staircase's cleaning been completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, I wanted to clean it properly, so it's taken some time....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please clean it carefully to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you to clean the reception hall thoroughly. Until you finish that, you will not be permitted any food or rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still dreaming that George-sama can help me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san is still as clumsy as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam has been in a bad mood since this morning. You could have held your head down in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People like that can go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning the reception hall will be tough. I'll help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but if Kanon-kun is punished too, I will be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying that you'll help is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood. Do your best, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to my foolish words, Beatrice-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am incompetent and uneducated furniture, so I am not qualified for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if that's the case, then why was I given a heart that can know love?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's going to be this hard and painful, I wish I'd never been given this heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Giving a heart to furniture, what an amusing thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans have been continually searching for the elements that make up the world since before the Christian Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a single man appeared, guided by a star,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally explained the single true element that makes up the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I am Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after thousands of years, the first expression that humans show when they see the me remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your worries are due to love. Adam and Eve learned love. They were kicked out of paradise, and they became human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you have known love, you are no longer furniture. You are now "human".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a long time since I have spoken with a human. I shall apologize for my talkativeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it is not a suitable apology, I will grant that desire of yours with my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am offering to bring you and the one you love together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Re...Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Request?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know that there are small torii and shrine built on the reef close to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to break the mirror kept inside that shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take action and break that mirror for me, as a reward, I will grant you your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a very good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, you may change your wish, and I can give you all of the gold I bestowed upon Kinzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a reason, let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but to this day, the island has been in peace, and nothing has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even if I don't break the mirror, this peace should continue into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's how it is. As you said, I can make an absolute guarantee about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The same unbreakable days that have passed until today will continue into tomorrow, and the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even imagining that you and Ushiromiya George could be joined is sinful, and foolish, foolish, foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish, foolish, know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for being a bit too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But the promise just now will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need my power, you can summon me at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappear, and don't ever show yourself in front of Shannon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...In parting, I shall leave a single souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A butterfly brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to decide your future of your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, furniture!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.97,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I fulfilled my promise with the witch in order to make my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeeh!? A young couple going on an overnight trip and you didn't even kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dating, but we're not married yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like that have to be done after you've sworn an oath before God.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a boyfriend toooo!! I can't believe Shannon got ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady is a wonderful person, so I'm sure a wonderful person will appear very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to console me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You traitor, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon, tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my hair or something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the way I talk after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady is already a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:23:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm the only one who can't get a boyfriend. All my friends have boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone said that this cultural festival, they'll bring their boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so sure I'd have a boyfriend before then,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't find a boyfriend. Only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for sobbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.82,0:23:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon, it's about time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't go quickly, Genji-san and Mom will get mad. Hurry, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I also... want to fall...in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon. How long have you been watering the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I- I am very sorry, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it... I don't see any progress since last I checked-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.56,0:24:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You don't want to hear my reprimand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't say more. You will finish all your work by the end of today. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.74,0:24:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry. That prank went a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.17,0:24:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you for a long time. What happened after?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.35,0:24:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y- yes. Thanks to you, it's going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, my magic is instantaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.69,0:24:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do forgive me. More importantly, I heard, I heard! About your trip alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was quite fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeees!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Th... that's right. Umm, Beatrice-sama. I bought some sweets as a souvenir from the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A souvenir for a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.36,0:25:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What interesting refreshments, thank you for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I shall treat you to a taste of Nero's Dolce Vita.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.10,0:25:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's alright. This is enough for me, so I'll give it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.64,0:25:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is yours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can treasure this as proof of our friendship, that would comfort me a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to, you can also gift it to someone suffering in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.64,0:25:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.42,0:25:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, by the way, can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.38,0:25:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can some people see Beatrice-sama, but others can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.45,0:25:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has something that resembles a wavelength, and it makes a big difference whether or not you can perceive between witches and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.31,0:25:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... what about the Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.97,0:25:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinzo is the same. There is no one with a more pitiful lack of magical talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.50,0:25:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:26:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept studying by himself like mad, and reached the level of magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.41,0:26:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the Master summoned Beatrice-sama with the power of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.69,0:26:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really just my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.63,0:26:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.25,0:26:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he was so full of enthusiasm, I generously responded and gave him a mountain of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.76,0:26:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Master... used that gold and succeeded in business, and grew his wealth into what it is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.90,0:26:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and then after obtaining every dream that could be obtained in the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.47,0:26:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he began to seek the single element that makes up the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.44,0:26:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.62,0:26:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks to that, I'm in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been sewn in place on this island for several decades now, invisible for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.99,0:26:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you helped me smash that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.53,0:26:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is that mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.87,0:26:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, it seems various things happened on the islands around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.05,0:27:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, bad things gathered, drawn towards an evil distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.01,0:27:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that a traveling eastern magician or something built a shrine for the repose of souls and sealed them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.33,0:27:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not its target. But it was a divine mirror. As a result, my power was sealed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.17,0:27:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds have come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.55,0:27:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When the ocean loses its splendor, it's just a grey puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.47,0:27:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? I think the ocean is a beautiful deep blue, even if it gets cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.98,0:27:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,These have been some unusual snacks. Now, it's almost time for you to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.43,0:27:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, someone doesn't like it when you drink tea with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.07,0:27:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.59,0:27:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun, Shannon. Tell me more about George at our next tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.53,0:27:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My magical power is still quite lacking. It's tiring even to show myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.16,0:28:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're that tired, never appear again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.13,0:28:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.50,0:28:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, didn't I tell you that you shouldn't hang around with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.10,0:28:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama isn't that bad of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.42,0:28:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not human,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.84,0:28:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.19,0:28:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We are furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not... furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.93,0:28:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We are furniture! We are less than human.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.88,0:28:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, you're acting like you've forgotten that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.26,0:28:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.88,0:28:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning, we have been unqualified to love or be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.12,0:28:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, you've just been tempted by that witch, and mistakenly believe that you became human!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.92,0:28:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that we are inferior to human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.08,0:28:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we could replace that unfulfilled part... wouldn't that mean that we could become human?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.82,0:28:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That couldn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.82,0:28:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.41,0:28:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea. Kanon-kun, what color does the sea look to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.26,0:29:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vague, dark-gray color.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.05,0:29:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks deep blue to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.17,0:29:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I understand, and you do not, that's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.36,0:29:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.55,0:29:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun. Would you stick out your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.44,0:29:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... hers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.37,0:29:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is mine. So think of it as me and treat it with respect, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.42,0:29:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.19,0:29:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This charm holds true magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.26,0:29:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that it will teach you an important emotion, Kanon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.85,0:29:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea full of the world's first element would be a very deep blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.03,0:29:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun will definitely be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.11,0:29:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After all-
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.14,0:29:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Without love, it cannot be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.74,0:30:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.36,0:30:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.22,0:30:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.77,0:30:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is heavy. Will it get worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.60,0:30:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the forecast says so. Should I bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.78,0:30:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unnecessary. You should leave me alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.59,0:30:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am busy on a journey through my own thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.00,0:30:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...Certainly. Then, if you would excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.45,0:30:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooohhh, Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.40,0:30:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...Why, why does my hand not reach Beatrice's smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.35,0:30:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do to be resurrected? What do you do to be smiling at me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.93,0:30:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to see your face again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.94,0:30:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You... stay away from the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.43,0:30:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, Kinzo... Can't you see me, even though I am here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.36,0:30:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I have to do to get my hands on your smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.22,0:31:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the age of the moon? The cycle of the comet? Is it the arrangement of the planets? What is lacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.23,0:31:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is, what is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.15,0:31:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, Kinzo. ...Without love, it cannot be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.90,0:31:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...Would I be able see something I couldn't have seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.47,0:31:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Without love, it cannot be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we are also furniture that could not become human.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.38,0:31:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kanon-kun... actually, I'd like to ask you a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.00,0:31:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning Jessie!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.90,0:32:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessieee! Is your boyfriend here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.10,0:32:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.75,0:32:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it seems he's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.00,0:32:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's busy with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.97,0:32:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is Jessie's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.70,0:32:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At least give us a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.46,0:32:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome, he's a working man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.38,0:32:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Suits? Glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.08,0:32:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about finding someone to pretend to be Milady's boyfriend and take him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,F- fake? Wh-who...?! I can't think of, anyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.70,0:32:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, what about Kanon-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.31,0:32:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun?! No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.28,0:32:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice? This is an opportunity to hangout with Kanon!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.11,0:32:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.93,0:32:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but, but, but, BUT...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.50,0:32:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,AaaahhHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.47,0:32:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessie, we have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.76,0:32:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Could it be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.99,0:33:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.90,0:33:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know where the stairs were. I apologize for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.90,0:33:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,R- right, umm... that outfit suits you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.30,0:33:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouta boyfriend is heeere!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.94,0:33:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...What should I do, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.71,0:33:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Milady!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.10,0:33:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He calls himself "boku" and she makes him call her Milady, like a butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.80,0:33:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun, could you close your eyes for just three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.90,0:33:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.14,0:33:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go to the stage! I have to get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.21,0:33:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...School?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.34,0:33:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a noisy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.30,0:33:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's important to always stay composed and dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.94,0:34:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, seeing Milady just now... I can understand Natsuhi's headache a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.20,0:34:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Madame Natsuhi, as PTA president, should have attended the ceremony in the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.27,0:34:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to see Milady's performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.78,0:34:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.16,0:34:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.85,0:34:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If a girl starts talking to you, all you have to say are these magic words!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.90,0:34:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.60,0:34:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.70,0:34:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,God, this might be my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.30,0:34:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My masochistic blood is boiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.60,0:34:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.60,0:34:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the book said!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.30,0:34:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.35,0:34:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never coming here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.28,0:34:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.32,0:36:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I... hate fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.87,0:36:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I really want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.93,0:36:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.53,0:36:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.96,0:37:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you everyone, enjoy the rest of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.36,0:37:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The young lady on stage is not at all like what the young lady of Ushiromiya should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.72,0:37:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But watching Milady have so much fun, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.60,0:37:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the true form of Ushiromiya Jessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.74,0:37:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked close to Milady, saw her in all seasons, and I thought I knew everything about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.16,0:38:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was only limited to one side of her, Milady of Rokkenjima.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.97,0:38:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are furniture. We serve on Rokkenjima, and live out our lives on Rokkenjima.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.54,0:38:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, I feel like I can see something that 'cannot be seen' on Rokkenjima.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.86,0:38:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Without love, it cannot be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.01,0:38:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't think of the ocean as blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.38,0:38:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, look, it's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.98,0:38:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica, you once again bought something with no taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.37,0:38:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, today Mira and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.55,0:38:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always told you to choose your friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.45,0:38:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.25,0:38:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get dressed. The piano teacher is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.68,0:39:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your awareness as a member of the Ushiromiya family is far from enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.70,0:39:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate studying and thick books that took away all my fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.13,0:39:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing I hated the most was myself that giving up every day like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.05,0:39:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Jessica - wasn't the cultural festival today?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.41,0:39:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.90,0:39:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching. You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.85,0:39:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.65,0:39:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You appeared with both composure and dignity. Fitting behavior for the students' representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience of standing above people and bearing responsibility will definitely be useful in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.02,0:39:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Krauss-sama, the guests are already waiting in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.74,0:39:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I'll be there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.32,0:39:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, even if she came, she would definitely say something like "it wasn't appropriate for the successor to the Ushiromiya family".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.68,0:40:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.01,0:40:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! Kanon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.00,0:40:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming to cheer me on today!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.16,0:40:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your singing... it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.55,0:40:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.03,0:40:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahahaha, really? I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.33,0:40:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sing, because I'm furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.67,0:40:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun, enough with that phrase "because I am furniture".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.56,0:40:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a human just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.01,0:40:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.60,0:40:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun, when you saw me singing... what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.15,0:40:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like you were having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.24,0:40:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... not completely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.68,0:40:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.68,0:40:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were jealous, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.12,0:40:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.48,0:40:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm the successor to the Ushiromiya family or something... I'm sure there'll be a lot of annoying stuff to do in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.35,0:40:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just gotta resign myself to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.96,0:40:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.25,0:41:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's one place where you and I are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.68,0:41:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.95,0:41:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept this kind of fate, so I do the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.59,0:41:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've created another self that can do everything I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.94,0:41:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,People are always making another part of themselves inside themselves that they can really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.46,0:41:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside themselves...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.42,0:41:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon is the name given to you in the Gospel House. It's not your real name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.90,0:41:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.60,0:41:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it should be alright to have times when you're Kanon-kun, and times when you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.24,0:41:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can live much, much more freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.92,0:41:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A time when, I am not Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.95,0:41:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't mind, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.43,0:41:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.47,0:42:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.90,0:42:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.34,0:42:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I did have a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.85,0:42:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The only truth now is that here, I am Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.96,0:42:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop that! You're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.66,0:42:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.95,0:42:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.55,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady, you are human!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.47,0:42:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's cruel to ask furniture to talk about dreams like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.76,0:42:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are you saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.63,0:42:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon told me. Something about Milady taking a liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.73,0:42:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.90,0:42:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I can't pretend to be a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.70,0:42:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot delude myself like Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.10,0:42:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.33,0:42:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,People cannot love furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.70,0:42:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Milady can love furniture, I cannot love Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.06,0:42:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.80,0:42:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If your feelings for me are due to my conceit, then please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.30,0:43:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you so much for treating me as human.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.43,0:43:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.33,0:43:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.93,0:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am also...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.96,0:43:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't go back to my room, mom will get mad at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.93,0:43:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you a good night, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.53,0:43:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.10,0:43:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, making a woman cry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.40,0:43:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Had you answered normally, another pair of lovers would have been born with my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.80,0:43:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.26,0:43:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just a demon who enjoys showing love to those who can never be joined, and deceiving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.83,0:43:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Furniture is a thoroughly pitiful existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.03,0:44:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon and George will also eventually reach a stalemate with their love, an ending that suits the tastes of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.10,0:44:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.85,0:44:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't think I would lend them that power without any compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.20,0:44:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lend a hand in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.06,0:44:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My compensation shall be one ticket to watch the cruel fate that the two of them will eventually meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.21,0:44:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after one thousand years, no better show exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.91,0:44:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at Kinzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.11,0:44:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a witch! Disappear and get out of my sight, you demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.64,0:44:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall disappear without being asked. My power still hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.58,0:44:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a low tide without the moon, my magical power will surely rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.18,0:44:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will surely have my return, at a time that is appropriate for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.22,0:44:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and rule as the true master of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.52,0:44:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, the door to the Golden Land will be opened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.09,0:45:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The covetous and greedy shall call me forth without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.46,0:45:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.79,0:45:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you leave me alone in this sea of suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.30,0:45:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I yearn after you this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.10,0:45:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, drinking any more will be damaging to your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.80,0:45:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Be silent, Genji. You do not understand, you do not understand my grief and sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.65,0:45:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Furniture, Furniture? How ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.05,0:45:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave me alone, Beatrice?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.95,0:45:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, two seeds of love have been sown.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.85,0:45:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the one already sown, that makes three.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.29,0:45:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing how they ripen!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.27,0:46:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.43,0:46:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean what I said. I still haven't built up my castle. Once I think of myself as an adult for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.57,0:46:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.47,0:46:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to give you an engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.80,0:46:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Engagement...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.83,0:46:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will probably bring a ring to the family conference coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.68,0:46:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I want you to let me hear your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.01,0:46:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you accept, I will proclaim our marriage to all of the relatives, including Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.74,0:46:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.31,0:46:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone says, I will make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.28,0:46:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.31,0:47:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Maria. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.71,0:47:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu-uu! I want Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.41,0:47:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to dress up like a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.91,0:47:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The family conference isn't for playing. We're going to meet Grandfather, so you have to wear western clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.88,0:47:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Halloween! Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.41,0:47:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat! Trick or treat! Uu-uu-uu-!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.44,0:47:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop saying "Uu-uu"!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.24,0:47:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For the lovely Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.51,0:47:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu-!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.44,0:47:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a sweet, got a sweet! Look, look, Mama, Mama! Happy Hallowee~n!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.91,0:47:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Maria, you can't just accept sweets from strangers, right? Return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.74,0:47:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, ho ho ho. She's a lovely young lady. How old is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.31,0:47:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, give the candy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.34,0:47:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu-! Uu-!! Maria got that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.91,0:47:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.88,0:47:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.58,0:47:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.70,0:47:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu-uu-!! No, Maria's candy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.61,0:47:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria's candy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.37,0:47:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't I always tell you not to say uu-uu-!!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.71,0:47:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.95,0:48:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu-uu, Mama, it hurts! Uu-uu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.61,0:48:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm telling you to shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.77,0:48:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason you can't make friends in class, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.65,0:48:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still crying? Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.07,0:48:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, it hurts...! Mama, save me...! Uu-uu-uu-uu-!!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.76,0:48:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're like this that Papa's business trip doesn't end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.11,0:48:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.84,0:48:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... done it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.80,0:48:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! Mama, come back...! \N\N\N-uu-uu-uu-!!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.40,0:48:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, I'm sorry... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.43,0:48:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama... welcome back...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.50,0:48:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive your bad Mama... I'm really sorry! Please, don't hate your Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.61,0:48:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama was only being possessed by an evil witch again... But, Mama came back, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.90,0:48:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...Do you want to celebrate Halloween, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.96,0:48:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wanted to show the pumpkin marshmallow to George onii-chan and Jessica onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.27,0:49:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.82,0:49:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they sell it in this town or not, but let's get off and try searching for it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.10,0:49:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu, ...yeah! Love you so much Mama, love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.01,0:49:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Maria. Maybe we won't find a marshmallow exactly like that one, but it's alright if there's a similar sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.67,0:49:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If it's a sweet I bought together with Mama, anything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.73,0:49:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, what are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.99,0:49:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.43,0:49:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finishing all of today's preparations. For now, shall we relax and wait while drinking tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.24,0:49:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm always pushing all my problems on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.17,0:49:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, can't you rely on me more?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.44,0:49:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.09,0:49:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I'm grateful for you always coming to my aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.21,0:50:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to get through today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.58,0:50:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The topic of Father's inheritance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.36,0:50:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay with Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.47,0:50:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. Genji and Doctor Nanjo are on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.65,0:50:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never allow those greedy siblings to meet Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.98,0:50:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the kitchen is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.56,0:50:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.32,0:50:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave everything to me, Gohda.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.02,0:50:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All the relatives will come visit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.60,0:50:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See that you do not make any blunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.70,0:50:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will keep in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.89,0:50:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.97,0:50:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we welcome an important guest in the truest sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.40,0:50:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.43,0:51:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.89,0:51:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.80,0:51:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The lawyer said that the situation is pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.80,0:51:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew this would happen, I wouldn't have started this many projects in the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.40,0:51:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.31,0:51:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, calm down, you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.01,0:51:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we gather the money, we'll be able to settle everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.56,0:51:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure it out. If it goes well, I'll treat you all to a champagne tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.31,0:51:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So just shut up and follow me, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.80,0:51:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes president!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.80,0:51:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.74,0:51:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well... has Rosa not arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.93,0:51:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. She is pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.97,0:51:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, because of the typhoon, the flight was delayed, but she's still too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.99,0:52:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As a brother, you still treat your sister as a child no matter how old you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.44,0:52:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! Dad's always a kid, no matter how old he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.04,0:52:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? If I was a kid, you'd be a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.50,0:52:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that! Are you seriously a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.20,0:52:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Six years later, you're still my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.04,0:52:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What you did to mom six years ago, I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.10,0:52:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun, let's not talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.58,0:52:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.01,0:52:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so slow, Rosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.59,0:52:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoh, Maria-chan! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.90,0:52:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, it's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.29,0:52:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that Battler-kun? He's really grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.74,0:52:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone I've met today had to say that once! How embarassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.60,0:52:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.09,0:52:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I saw you, you were three years old. You don't remember me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.01,0:52:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, this is Battler onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.26,0:52:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Rudolf's son. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.44,0:52:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.55,0:52:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that must be for Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.99,0:52:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu-uu! Halloween, Halloween! Battler knows about that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.72,0:52:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you have to call him Battler onii-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.62,0:53:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.30,0:53:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.30,0:53:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.23,0:53:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.13,0:53:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Halloween, what about costumes? What does Maria want to dress up as?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.34,0:53:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! The witch, Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.64,0:53:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Bea? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.61,0:53:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.52,0:53:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry up, we're going to leave you guys behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.22,0:53:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, okay, Maria, let's hurry. Woosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.22,0:53:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Woooooosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.93,0:53:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Milady, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.23,0:53:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumasawa-san. When the day of the family conference comes, for some reason, I feel curious about this witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.23,0:53:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.30,0:53:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The family conference is the day when everyone related to Grandfather gathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.70,0:53:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that Battler is also coming today after six years?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.23,0:54:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if there might be relatives who have not appeared in decades showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.33,0:54:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is such a thing, this year's family conference will become like a typhoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.13,0:54:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumasawa-san, you know more about Beatrice, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.00,0:54:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I can say is that Beatrice-sama is the Witch of Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.40,0:54:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the other master who controls the night of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.99,0:54:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just second hand talk from Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.18,0:54:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I can at least say this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.20,0:54:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.10,0:54:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In ancient times, Rokkenjima was feared, and called Azukijima (Evil Appetite Island).
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.64,0:54:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The story told among the fishermen is that "Azuki" was a mispronunciation of "Akujiki."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.80,0:54:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also heard that. The fishermen were afraid because of the sunken rocks and shipwrecks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.70,0:55:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, a traveling mountaineering ascetic or someone built that shrine, reposed the souls and settled them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.73,0:55:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That shrine for the repose of souls was destroyed by an eerie violet thunderbolt this summer, which tore up the darkness of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.89,0:55:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil spirits of Akujikishima woke up from their sleep, and summoned Beatrice-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.84,0:55:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.30,0:55:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If Beatrice-sama happened to come for the family conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.55,0:55:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If she happened to come...?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.90,0:55:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you don't plan on appearing at the family conference this year either?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.93,0:55:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to join in on the argument of those vultures.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.24,0:55:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I will... hold a certain ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.64,0:55:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.87,0:56:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be more accurate to call it a gamble... Because miracles do not dwell in magic that doesn't bear risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.77,0:56:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So as your friend, I can only pray from the bottom of my heart that you will win this ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.58,0:56:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, Kinzo-san. Did you hear that a longed-for guest will be at the family meeting this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.43,0:56:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.29,0:56:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Battler-kun from Rudolf-san's family. I hear he will be coming after six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.24,0:56:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Battler? I wouldn't call him 'longed for', a guest who doesn't show up for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.34,0:56:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibly, a truly longed-for guest... will pay us a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.88,0:56:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything depends on the results of the roulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.69,0:56:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.01,0:56:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Genji speaking. Everyone has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.90,0:56:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In total, 18 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.87,0:56:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, all the pieces are lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.61,0:56:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.08,0:57:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.59,0:57:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you tell me you don't have a plan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.33,0:57:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know what you're going to do before you know what you're going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.74,0:57:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I don't know your moves, I don't have any plan. Feel free to take the initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.18,0:57:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... in what way shall I destroy your defense? With how many moves will I checkmate you? It's an opportunity to display my skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.68,0:57:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever moves you come at me with, I won't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.74,0:57:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I stand my ground on that point, I won't lose. The way this game is made, you cannot win!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.88,0:57:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right. However, you know what? I'll decide how many times we'll repeat this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.70,0:57:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be repeated over and over again, until I win and you recognize your defeat, okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.62,0:57:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, this is torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.02,0:57:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Beatrice... I have only one thing to tell you before we start.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.38,0:57:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.28,0:57:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, whether I'll believe you or not, is something I'll decide for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.07,0:58:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You think this is torture for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.35,0:58:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.28,0:58:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what are you talking about...!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.27,0:58:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, you will yield to me and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.15,0:58:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, this is torture for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.59,0:58:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How amusing, a fine metaphor!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.16,0:58:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come then.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.68,0:58:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall begin that torture,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.35,0:58:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Urshiromiya Battleeeeeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.49,0:58:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, not much is different this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.86,0:58:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! This is from Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.84,0:58:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.16,0:58:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aniki, why do you think Maria likes Halloween so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.72,0:58:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, well, she is the 'witch' Maria-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.52,0:58:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.17,0:58:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, is there some relation between witches and Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.59,0:58:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Battler...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.08,0:58:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! The ancient Celts thought the sun would die at the end of October.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.90,0:58:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, after resting its body in the land of the dead, it would resurrect again on the winter solstice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.79,0:59:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They called the day that the sun ended its one year lifespan and died New Year's Eve, or Samhain.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.10,0:59:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoh! Even I never knew Halloween had such a history.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.61,0:59:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! So Halloween is the time when the power of witches and demons is at its most vigorous and prosperous!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.30,0:59:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Beatrice will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.91,0:59:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, we'll eat marshmallow candies together, and she'll bring Maria to the Golden Land with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.81,0:59:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Uu!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.22,0:59:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, isn't that wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.97,0:59:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Rosa, how old is Maria this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.72,0:59:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, stop talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.53,0:59:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda-san, can you take everyone to the guest house?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.73,0:59:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Well then, everyone, I will guide you to the guesthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.21,0:59:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.76,0:59:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.04,0:59:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm always telling you not to talk about witches... Haven't I always said that was our promise together...?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.02,0:59:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, it hurts, Mama, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.23,0:59:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so noisy with that 'Halloween, Halloween'... ridiculous, isn't it? You're nine years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.78,1:00:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We were even late because I bought that disgusting monster marshmallow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.63,1:00:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more will you have to embarrass me before you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.77,1:00:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting, disgusting! That's what you are, that's what you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.87,1:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Mama... Save me, Mama... Beat the bad witch...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.83,1:00:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop saying witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.07,1:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Mama...!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.58,1:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just stay there doing that forever!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.98,1:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria-sama, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.96,1:00:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.83,1:00:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a horrible person. I can't believe that was a mother...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.98,1:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. Maria can handle that much. Maria is just fine...!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.13,1:00:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll exchange it for something I received earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.19,1:00:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this was from Rosa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.41,1:00:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it would be easy for Beatrice to repair it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.55,1:00:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria-sama... you know about Beatrice?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.83,1:01:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Maria is friends with Beatrice. Why don't we meet her today and play?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.35,1:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Father said that he was very busy with his research. He said that, unfortunately, he will be unable to make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.85,1:01:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief. He's really not attending this year?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.92,1:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nanjo. Is it really a problem with his research and his mood?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.90,1:01:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't already bedridden, and unable to get up, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.35,1:01:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I wonder. There is not much I can say...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.72,1:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is steadily regaining his health.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.60,1:01:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Although if he's that energetic, I wish he'd at least come to greet us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.62,1:01:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.55,1:01:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were here, you would complain the whole time about how you couldn't relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.50,1:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you two quickly become respectful of Father now that his remaining life has been announced?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.23,1:01:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.36,1:01:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it, Aneki.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.90,1:01:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a few things that the siblings couldn't talk to him about before forming a unified opinion, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.00,1:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! We must take this precious time seriously and talk together modestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.60,1:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.80,1:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your precious, important talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.80,1:02:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria-chan really has grown a lot this past year.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.12,1:02:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it look that way?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.80,1:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.66,1:02:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because she has such an affectionate mother with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.80,1:02:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I...am not qualified to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.65,1:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Children can't choose their parents. That poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.52,1:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that go both ways?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.83,1:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A parent can't choose what kind of child is born, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.95,1:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't a matter of who is at fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.89,1:02:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't everything alright as long as you slowly watch over her as she grows up, with living together on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.52,1:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria-chan has grown up a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.45,1:02:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.77,1:02:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it raining?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.32,1:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... I told her,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.42,1:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just stay there doing that forever."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.21,1:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But she must have already...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.51,1:02:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria is that kind of child!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.90,1:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.23,1:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.34,1:03:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.25,1:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let her be. More importantly, should we continue?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.62,1:03:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.42,1:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria! Are you here? If you're here, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.52,1:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.90,1:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.05,1:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.03,1:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.15,1:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama isn't bad... She was just possessed by a bad witch again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.13,1:03:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Mama lost to the bad witch, forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.03,1:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like Mama. I love you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.30,1:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Maria. Why don't you come back to the mansion with Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.17,1:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu — I'm not coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.25,1:03:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.97,1:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Beatrice. She'll come really soon. So I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.33,1:03:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Then instead of waiting here, why don't we wait in the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.87,1:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Beatrice will co-me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.37,1:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she does, I'll give a candy to Beatrice. I'll do trick-or-treat!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.44,1:03:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give her a jack-o-lantern marshmallow candy and say Happy Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.74,1:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uuuuuuuuuuuuuu—!!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.84,1:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.03,1:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. Have you been healthy?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.70,1:04:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu—! Maria is well! Beatrice, Happy Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.70,1:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Happy Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.47,1:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The candy has become like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.56,1:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —, stepped on and smashed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.86,1:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can Beato return it to normal?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.11,1:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.78,1:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Maria. Close your eyes and try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.64,1:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of candy was it really?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.90,1:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.70,1:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You may now open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.68,1:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice is always awesome, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.67,1:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my face look familiar? If you stare so fixedly, you might burn a hole through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.86,1:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.39,1:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria. I will give this to you in exchange for that sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.11,1:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —, letter?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.18,1:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The time will soon come that you may open it, but until then, you definitely must not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.67,1:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It will become an invitation calling you to the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.62,1:05:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden Land! Finally take Maria there! Uu —!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.50,1:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this, is for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.51,1:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... dad's special envelope!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.54,1:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I have met you here probably means that you were chosen by Kinzo's roulette.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.98,1:05:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, then read its contents aloud while seated at the dinner table, when all of the siblings are gathered.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.78,1:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.23,1:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us meet later.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.43,1:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to name myself in that place.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.37,1:05:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been awaiting you... Beatrice-sama.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.01,1:05:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Genji. Is Kinzo well?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.81,1:05:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He is very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.27,1:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us greet him. It will be good to hurl curses at each other after thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.95,1:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.49,1:06:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudolf's second wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.25,1:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.80,1:06:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kyrie.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.45,1:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this is our first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.20,1:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you have a vague idea, you dare to ask my name?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.60,1:06:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since he left this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.20,1:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it has already been several years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.23,1:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he want to make me a bird in a cage that much? How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.25,1:06:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.25,1:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? A magic ward! Is that person unable to get by without relying on something like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.24,1:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I open it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.87,1:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.13,1:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to enjoy the final gamble and fall of an aged mage, who fell in love with me and threw away all his life!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.89,1:07:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to enjoy my game with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.39,1:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... I have brought lunch, Beatrice-sama.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.86,1:07:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a long time... Furniture called Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.58,1:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It has... been a long time...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.56,1:07:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to resolve my final promise with Kinzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.18,1:07:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your final promise with... Master?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.93,1:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I lent Kinzo a mountain of gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.28,1:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When Kinzo gives that up, it will be returned to me with interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.35,1:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here tonight to receive that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.67,1:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be... You...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.90,1:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the sweetfish river running through my beloved hometown...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.60,1:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the witch's epitaph!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.30,1:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The day when everything will be returned to the Golden Land has come.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.46,1:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.80,1:08:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The day when the shame of your time as furniture will end has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.42,1:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.20,1:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Shannon will now have emotions that she must not know,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.76,1:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and will probably have a very hard time forced upon her.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.09,1:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of attachment is the greatest joy for a witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.40,1:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for gifting us furniture the day of our release.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.32,1:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I hate you for making this day difficult for Shannon to accept!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.55,1:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me, try to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.40,1:08:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you kill me, the day of rest for the furniture will not come for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.60,1:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want that,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.81,1:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.23,1:08:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel and kiss my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.70,1:08:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll leave this place and never show myself again for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.63,1:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.33,1:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If the door to the Golden Land is opened, your life as furniture will end.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.37,1:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you desire, I will even give you life as a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.91,1:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it, you grew jealous seeing Shannon wallow in the swamp of sweet love.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.15,1:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are sorely tempted to know the taste of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.94,1:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, stop it! I won't be reduced to a toy to please you!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.02,1:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoh. Then I will be satisfied with Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.20,1:09:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the second twilight, those who remain shall tear apart the two who are close.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.61,1:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that there is no one more fitting to be a sacrifice for the second twilight than Shannon as she is now?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.98,1:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dirty...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.50,1:09:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Kanon?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.84,1:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kneel, I'll surely hold back from choosing Shannon as a sacrifice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.38,1:10:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What the shit is this? This is just demented!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.52,1:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because your argument regarding 18 or 19 people, which you are using as a basis to deny me, is truly humorous.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.35,1:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So much so that I tried changing my move.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.71,1:10:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can accept something like this, right?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.37,1:10:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch came in, walking right through the entrance hall, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.22,1:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.51,1:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? In the last game, I let you make your moves terribly freely, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.32,1:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give in already after the first move?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.14,1:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This much isn't even close to enough to make me accept something like a witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.58,1:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now you only made it look like you had fixed Maria's candy with magic. It's not magic!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.19,1:11:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Is that your move in response to mine?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.24,1:11:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.10,1:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've dug your own grave, Ushiromiya Battler.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.62,1:11:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to continue my move. It has barely begun, the Turn of the Witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.97,1:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a big yawn, Battler-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.53,1:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the tension resolved, I started to get sleepy, listening to the sound of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.24,1:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —? Battler's asleep? A nap?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.30,1:11:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we've finally gathered all the cousins together after six years.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.10,1:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy doesn't have a clue that he's the main guest of this family conference, does he?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.23,1:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've casually eaten lunch, and there's even a typhoon and rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.36,1:12:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we aren't doing anything, that means it isn't my turn yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.87,1:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always the main character of your own life, right? Why are you acting like a supporting actor?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.64,1:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's already backstage.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.65,1:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pretend not to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.95,1:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's got that kind of personality where he doesn't want to get up on the stage because he can't be the main character.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.83,1:12:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-chan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.23,1:12:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to get up on the stage?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.02,1:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like around 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.92,1:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her my name, but she didn't tell me hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.12,1:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this person trying to say that she was... the witch of the portrait?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.55,1:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen a blonde woman like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.95,1:12:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.02,1:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If this woman claims to be Beatrice, what is her purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.57,1:12:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious! She'll insist she's a legitimate successor of the inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.62,1:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is still a slave to Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.80,1:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If they had that daughter, he'd hand over the whole fortune to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.09,1:13:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe she plans to call herself his mistress's daughter, and demand that the inheritance be distributed to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.15,1:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We desperately need a large amount of money urgently because of our circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.47,1:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyrie, could you use the chessboard thinking to reason out her goal?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.50,1:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first I've heard of it, but one of the premises here is that we have an urgent need to collect money, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.50,1:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.31,1:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.50,1:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Her unexpected visit was kept hidden from us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.85,1:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what her surprise is, but she's been hiding it until today.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.38,1:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that, it seems her goal is one that would be disadvantageous to her if we did interact.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.67,1:13:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. If she had a will or something that could prove that she was acknowledged as a blood relative...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.16,1:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If she thought it was rock-solid proof, then you'd think she'd actually have announced it beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.68,1:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that would mean that, from the time she first aimed for a surprise attack, we know the enemy couldn't win in a frontal attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.79,1:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To skip to the conclusion, it will probably be something related either directly or indirectly to the inheritance problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.86,1:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this carries with it a significant impact, it is not absolute.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.96,1:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, no matter what our opponent brings up, we interact calmly, without rushing things.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.10,1:14:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What I don't know about is the connection between her and Krauss nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.39,1:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If Krauss nii-san called her here, it might make things troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.15,1:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's handle it like this. As long as she can't clearly prove her identity, we won't accept her position.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.05,1:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who she is, we won't admit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.67,1:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. In other words, whatever is shown to us now on Rokkenjima cannot be accepted as true.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.19,1:14:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She will have to wait until the typhoon goes away and prove it to us at the proper place.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.35,1:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Recklessly finding fault in that kind of thing is Aneki's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.40,1:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We all need money urgently!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.00,1:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we let our hopes to get the inheritance be crushed by a mysterious woman like this?!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.35,1:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria. Today at noon, who was that woman we met outside?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.55,1:15:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —... I've said it many times, she's Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.16,1:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, have you ever met Beatrice before, at this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.97,1:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! We meet every year.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.09,1:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.38,1:15:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she live here?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.94,1:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! Beatrice lives on this island because she is the witch of Rokkenjima.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.29,1:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, even when there is no family meeting she's on this island, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.80,1:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu — ... Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.57,1:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be, it's unbelievable. When?...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.56,1:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived on this island. I spent my time in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.42,1:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I have never met a witch like that...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.46,1:15:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.47,1:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with my head?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.72,1:15:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, are you okay? Mama?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.95,1:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.11,1:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to the VIP room, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.94,1:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. I heard that the visitor is Beatrice-sama, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.17,1:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to open the doors to the Golden Land and return everything back there!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.26,1:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be, why now of all times?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.78,1:16:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? We are furniture!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.81,1:16:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we acted like humans, because of love... we can't obediently accept the day when our service is over!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.25,1:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.41,1:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She joined you together, planning to use you and George-sama as the sacrifices of the second twilight.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.26,1:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? By tempting you, Nee-san, she took advantage of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.74,1:16:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.83,1:16:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But she told me,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.59,1:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,she promised that if you don't accept the engagement ring tonight, she won't choose you as a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.53,1:16:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our salvation is in the Golden Land!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.99,1:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can make it that far, we can become human!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.64,1:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.04,1:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Together. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.38,1:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To start a real life.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.64,1:17:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, I wonder if I will be able to know love as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.94,1:17:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll stop making people cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.31,1:17:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I... don't want to be furniture anymore!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.28,1:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't apologize. I'm a witch, after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.51,1:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.24,1:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it, right? What saved your romance was my doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.54,1:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My sheer mischievious heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.41,1:17:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing more than a seed I sowed to see how it would twist and fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.34,1:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter your ulterior motive, you gave me the magic of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.71,1:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change this fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.61,1:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I won't hold a grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.58,1:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for teaching me to be human.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.84,1:18:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer furniture.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.14,1:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly frustrating, furniture.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.71,1:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not furniture.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.58,1:18:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Be silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.11,1:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.98,1:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally came to understand people like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.91,1:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm now sure that this is the way to resist you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.08,1:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.11,1:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.34,1:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will carry out the fate that has been given to me. So, I won't entertain you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.08,1:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do with you...?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.21,1:18:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's such a way to resist? I like it!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.28,1:18:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you, together with your beloved one!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.90,1:18:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is the fate that you have decided, that is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.00,1:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think that will bore me, that's a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.34,1:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That just made my interest in your final moments grow hotter and hotter!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.40,1:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Now if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.41,1:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.01,1:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting after all!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.92,1:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'm not so old yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.55,1:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I am still not tired of living after one thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.56,1:19:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's main course is calf steak.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.16,1:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To accompany, I have a Bordelaise sauce.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.90,1:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the red wine base I used was excellent even among those made in Bordeaux.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.83,1:20:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, I prepared an original blend of this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.16,1:20:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a blend of choice alcohol from around the world to further deepen the taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.96,1:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This sauce is limited to this year.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.67,1:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It would greatly please me if you were to enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.80,1:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.87,1:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Kyrie-sama!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.24,1:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 18 relatives and servants on this island...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.52,1:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but, I believe I heard a guest was coming today?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.72,1:20:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she wished to have her meal alone in the VIP room.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.81,1:20:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,VIP Room?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.71,1:20:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.81,1:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... Beatrice-sama.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.85,1:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice? Is this that Beatrice?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.85,1:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.38,1:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda, is that also some side show for the dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.42,1:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop with this cheap play. Aniki, you've called her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.95,1:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nii-san, let's be honest. Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.32,1:21:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you tell me that she is really the Beatrice of the portrait?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.78,1:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.28,1:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda, call for Genji right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.28,1:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Aniki, you don't know either?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.48,1:21:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, did Father call her here?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.55,1:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Could she be Father's mistress or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.80,1:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The head wouldn't have something as filthy as a mistress!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.42,1:21:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, where did that woman come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.18,1:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The only boat trip today was the one which brought you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.08,1:21:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how could you prove that there were no other boats besides the one we were on?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.48,1:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't prove "she didn't come"!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.25,1:21:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need someone to say they saw her to prove the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.25,1:21:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Kyrie met that woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.39,1:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.36,1:21:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible to prove "she didn't come".
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.29,1:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if everyone says they haven't seen her,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.19,1:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It is also impossible to deny the possibility that "she came secretly."
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.26,1:22:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So, that's the "Devil's proof", right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.03,1:22:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What we can be sure of is that she came to this manson with some kind of goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.86,1:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? She probably intends to claim right over Father's inheritance!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.36,1:22:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, wait a minute! Genji-san will be coming soon. He will definitely answer our questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.33,1:22:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put that aside until then.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.19,1:22:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like it's getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.43,1:22:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.99,1:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Kids, return to the guesthouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.58,1:22:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeeeeh?!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.26,1:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to prove a devil, as long as you meet one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.63,1:22:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's impossible to prove that one "doesn't exist".
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.66,1:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if no one's ever seen one, it's not evidence of "not existing."
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.67,1:22:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what I saw was...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.84,1:22:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry I'm late! I already called Genji here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.70,1:23:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Is there anything I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.50,1:23:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can. Plenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.20,1:23:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Genji-san, please answer honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.47,1:23:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that Beatrice in the VIP room now?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.84,1:23:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't expect that the witch Beatrice-sama would actually show up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.40,1:23:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nanjo and Grandfather have been friends for a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.24,1:23:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a person for Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.87,1:23:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a mistress?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.90,1:23:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.65,1:23:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.47,1:23:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I've never met her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.50,1:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that she passed away a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.57,1:23:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they have kids?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.37,1:23:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.47,1:23:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, Kinzo-san was always doing research to ressurrect Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.18,1:24:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had a child with his late mistress, he would probably shed all his love onto them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.58,1:24:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, those two probably didn't have a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.68,1:24:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also a "Devil's proof".
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.18,1:24:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way to prove it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.55,1:24:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it really be that the illegitimate child returned to the island to take revenge on Grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.35,1:24:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge? You've watched too many strange TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.75,1:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, but there are 18 people on this island.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.88,1:24:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is no way to do anything suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.05,1:24:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if you use the name of the witch,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.48,1:24:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What can one human woman who can't use magic even do?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.65,1:24:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Battler's understanding of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.51,1:24:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.08,1:24:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler doesn't believe the 19th guest, Beatrice, is a witch, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.08,1:24:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.21,1:24:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way witches exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.51,1:24:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's a "Devil's proof"! There is no way witches do exist?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.11,1:24:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only ask the Witch's side to make a rebuttal. This is also a Devils's proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.71,1:24:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If she shows herself, this will be all over.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.06,1:24:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us something that is impossible for a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.19,1:24:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.76,1:25:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, then Beatrice will surely show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.86,1:25:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Battler will believe in her as well right? In Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.39,1:25:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, then I'll believe it. I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.79,1:25:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, where is George-aniki?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.62,1:25:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that. Why are you also laughing?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.96,1:25:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.16,1:25:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait, Aniki, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.36,1:25:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayo,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.60,1:25:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.96,1:25:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this ring is for.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.86,1:25:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, George.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.51,1:25:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just looking at how you are now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.19,1:25:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gazing at you as you will be in the future too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.25,1:25:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You always tell me that, how you want to slowly grow old surrounded by healthy children and grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.40,1:25:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly spending the time while getting old.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.09,1:25:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we're old, you will be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.67,1:26:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I predicted this day would come
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.71,1:26:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show me that future.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.93,1:26:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise that even if we become souls, we will always be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.45,1:26:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.91,1:26:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I want you to put that ring on, whatever finger you like, and have that be your answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.68,1:26:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, so, by tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.92,1:26:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my answer, George-san.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.10,1:26:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.10,1:26:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no blessing from God, no pastor to witness, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.59,1:26:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But, two souls were joined here today...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.55,1:26:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.97,1:27:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you wear the ring even though you knew it would go unfulfilled?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.72,1:27:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, we agreed to be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.71,1:27:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant, our eternity was complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.82,1:27:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.45,1:27:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.81,1:27:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun, why do you want to be human?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.04,1:27:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, I liked Milady!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.20,1:27:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And after seeing Milady that day,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.30,1:27:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked her even more!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.40,1:27:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just afraid...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.00,1:27:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if love could not be eternal, I was better off without it!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.90,1:27:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama is detestable.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.22,1:27:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the witch's expectations are probably off.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.80,1:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.65,1:28:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing love isn't a regret that ties you to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.25,1:28:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the place we should reach on our journey through life...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.63,1:28:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no objections. Natsuhi and I accept it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.83,1:28:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.70,1:28:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I also accept it. No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.75,1:28:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I also accept. This is your victory.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.60,1:28:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've proven the devil.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.60,1:28:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyrie, do you still have any objections?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.25,1:28:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it unless everyone's together.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.60,1:28:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.75,1:28:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to accept you are the consultant alchemist of the Ushiromiya family, and a witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.86,1:28:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.63,1:29:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.16,1:29:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, it seems that I've escaped being one of the first sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.71,1:29:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then Beatrice, which six pieces did you take?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.04,1:29:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My defense is perfect, I will not shame myself like last time!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.65,1:29:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Genji-san?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.35,1:29:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.95,1:29:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for waking you this early.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.35,1:29:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... actually, at the chapel...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.68,1:30:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.75,1:30:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to the dining hall to clean up the tea set, there was a memo with 'chapel' written on it...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.65,1:30:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama... look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.15,1:30:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy HALLOWEEN for MARIA
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.43,1:30:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check on Maria and come back. Go tell Krauss nii-san and the rest!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.73,1:30:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to contact Krauss-sama, but could not find him...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.03,1:30:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you checked inside the chapel?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.76,1:30:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.89,1:30:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The chapel lock is special, so the master key does not work. Only a single key can open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.93,1:30:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that key is missing from the key box.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.14,1:30:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.10,1:30:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The time to open that will come soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.21,1:31:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.51,1:31:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.45,1:31:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you awake, Battler?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.51,1:31:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I felt like I saw something...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.52,1:31:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the sweetfish river running through my beloved hometown.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.09,1:31:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You who seek the Golden Land, follow its path downstream in search of the key.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.49,1:31:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I feel so uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.09,1:31:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the Witch's epitaph circling my mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.49,1:32:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who obtains the key must then travel to the Golden Land in accordance with these rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.82,1:32:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens... when you get there?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.36,1:32:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, why do I care about this kind of thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.19,1:32:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The game between us and the witch is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.79,1:32:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.13,1:32:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,On the first twilight, offer the six chosen by the key as sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.13,1:32:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Offer up the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.77,1:32:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart hurts...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.03,1:32:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to live anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.47,1:32:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.97,1:32:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for the chapel... Where did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.93,1:32:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.59,1:33:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.71,1:33:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.30,1:33:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.52,1:33:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambulance! Police!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.88,1:33:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.11,1:33:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,DON'T LOOK!!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.47,1:33:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!! Mother!!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.96,1:33:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why? When you denied my existence in the last game, you thought in a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.21,1:33:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Their faces are crushed, so the identities of the corpses cannot be confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.72,1:34:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the possibility that fake corpses had been prepared to create an alibi cannot be eliminated. Because of that, the human culprit theory can be maintained!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.96,1:34:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So this time I left the bodies intact. Oh, this makes it easy to narrow down the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.65,1:34:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drag out your guts!!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.56,1:34:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Battler, try to deny the corpses in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.05,1:34:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit could be human, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.26,1:34:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt your loved ones, deny the witch dancing in madness on the stage of blood!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.05,1:35:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying... Damn it, damn it, I won't cry!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.45,1:35:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we cry, the reality of what has happened here won't change.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.03,1:35:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, something's wrong within the mansion. The phone seems to be out of order. The emergency radio is not working either.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.40,1:35:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Does that mean we can't contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.29,1:35:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that person! They did something to the phone line, and killed Dad and Mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.51,1:35:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.25,1:35:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! Damn it, damn it, DAMN IT!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.28,1:35:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.98,1:36:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it has begun, Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.80,1:36:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like anyone can solve this riddle anyway. So Beato will definitely win.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.00,1:36:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and open the door to the Golden Land and take me away!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.20,1:36:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda-san, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.70,1:36:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.00,1:36:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll double-check the VIP room and go back to the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.10,1:36:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda-san. If you find her... tell me right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.71,1:36:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.90,1:36:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady... I'm afraid Beatrice has already-
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.50,1:36:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I read the message in the VIP room.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.07,1:37:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I'd be that senile, to just sit around here waiting for you to come barging in to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.25,1:37:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These stupid parents have now filled their bellies in the land of sweets!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.98,1:37:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.51,1:37:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.30,1:37:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad are gone...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.67,1:37:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the corridor. If you need something, please call me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.40,1:37:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah— ...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.30,1:37:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.58,1:37:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.00,1:37:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.30,1:37:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I am...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.80,1:37:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're furniture.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.32,1:37:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.56,1:38:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For the second twilight sacrifice, I will pick the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.06,1:38:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W- wait! That's not the kind of relationship we have!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.25,1:38:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then I will only kill Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.13,1:38:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.90,1:38:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.30,1:38:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? To see the pained look on your face. Why else?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.43,1:38:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.97,1:38:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me laugh as hard as I can, furniture of Kinzo!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.57,1:38:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady, I'm here to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.34,1:38:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you down to the hell you came from!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.61,1:38:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.07,1:38:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.01,1:39:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.61,1:39:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.05,1:39:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It seems that you're not all useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.80,1:39:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn, Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.60,1:39:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite an interesting show. I was going to let you get away. But now, your rudeness has caused me to change my mind...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.50,1:39:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you kill Milady!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.76,1:39:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk, furniture.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.50,1:39:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, furniture.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.23,1:39:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Know your place, furniture!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.73,1:39:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun isn't furniture, he is a human!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.09,1:39:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.61,1:39:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun... he rushed in to save me of his own will,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.91,1:39:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and he stood in the path of a fearsome witch, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.10,1:39:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.11,1:39:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-sacrifice is part the noble spirit that only humans have.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.41,1:40:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun is a human!!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.81,1:40:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't speak, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.65,1:40:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, arise, forgive the sin, one of the seven stakes of Purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.11,1:40:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Lust!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.52,1:40:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Asmodeus of Lust, right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.55,1:40:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this farce. Quickly, execute the second twilight. Don't keep me waiting, alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.27,1:40:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.24,1:40:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.00,1:40:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you scared? How cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.35,1:40:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, where do you want it? Where do you want me to pierce you? Answer me, cutie boy. Wherever you want it, I'll run you through hard!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.73,1:40:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.74,1:40:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, try to chase me, you blind idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.85,1:40:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.90,1:40:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.93,1:40:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess was... spot on...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.68,1:41:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you... right...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.55,1:41:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kanon?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.30,1:41:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Milady Jessica wasn't going to be killed before you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.20,1:41:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, that's it, that's it! That face, that look on your face is what I wanted to see!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.47,1:41:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How truly enjoyable!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.27,1:41:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, arise, forgive the sin, one of the seven stakes of Purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.61,1:41:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrath!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.65,1:41:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Satan of Wrath, right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.65,1:41:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That furniture, close the curtain on his stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.73,1:41:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not furniture anymore...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.10,1:41:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I won't doubt that again!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.53,1:41:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your chest... It's so warm, and it feels so good to pierce it, okay...? Come on, let me have another taste, alright...?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.54,1:41:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you make me feel good?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.31,1:42:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I couldn't... protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.50,1:42:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry... Kanon-kun... You aren't furniture anymore...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.52,1:42:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.30,1:42:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you... what your real name was...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.00,1:42:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My... real name is...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.00,1:42:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... became... human...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.20,1:42:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after a hundred years, furniture is furniture, fool! I'll tell you what it really means to disgrace the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.52,1:43:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so it has begun?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.55,1:43:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.58,1:43:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon. I shall be writing a will. Please copy what I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.80,1:43:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.05,1:43:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. If I am to speak of my life, I must begin writing from when I met that witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.79,1:43:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After Jessica flew out, we investigated the church where the tragedy occurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.06,1:43:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we found a letter on the table left by the witch.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.46,1:43:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In the letter, Beatrice declares she is taking everything that gave to Grandfather back with an interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.50,1:44:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The interest was everything that Grandfather had given birth to.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.87,1:44:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that all of Grandfather's grandchildren, including me, are included in the interest!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.70,1:44:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone solves the epitaph and discovers the hidden gold,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.77,1:44:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice shall renounce all rights to its recovery for all time. That is the special clause.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.95,1:44:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, next to the letter, there are three gold bars inscribed with the crest of the One-winged Eagle. These prove that Grandfather's gold legend is real.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.88,1:44:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the witch's letter of provocation.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.06,1:44:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This magic circle is...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.39,1:44:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the seventh magic circle of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.96,1:44:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hebrew words written around the circumference says
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.36,1:45:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"The lord has freed me from my chains, I will offer to you the sacrifice of thanksgiving, and will call on the name of the Lord."
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.46,1:45:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing Father and the rest was so that they could be sacrifices for this magic circle...?!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.62,1:45:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,HAPPY HALLOWEEN FOR... MARIA
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.08,1:45:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.59,1:45:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that why the key of this place was handed to Maria?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.76,1:45:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But why specifically choose the chapel?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.22,1:45:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa, is there any special meaning to this chapel?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.05,1:45:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Special meaning?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.16,1:45:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell whether she called the six of them over here before killing them, or whether she killed them before carrying them over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.52,1:45:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But either way, it would take a lot of effort and risk.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.27,1:45:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. In doing something that elaborate, there would be an extremely high chance that when the police came, some disadvantage evidence would be found.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.10,1:45:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there should be another meaning here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.93,1:45:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father wasn't a devout believer.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.72,1:45:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but he regards this place as sacred.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.07,1:46:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a long time ago he said that someday, he too might be able to receive a blessing there.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.67,1:46:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But unless a miracle occurred, that day would never come.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.10,1:46:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.80,1:46:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it means, but it seems like to Grandfather that a fate that had been decided ever since he built this chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.50,1:46:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.16,1:46:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.72,1:46:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.63,1:46:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,M, B, T, Q... That is an incredible probability.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.18,1:46:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it can't be done without a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.35,1:46:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that the door will only open in case of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.31,1:46:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be blessed only when a miracle occurs.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.50,1:46:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a chapel that won't open?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.78,1:46:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.95,1:46:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.94,1:46:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to this chapel...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.66,1:46:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Genji-san say there was only one key?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.96,1:46:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is only one key that is usually kept in the key box in the servants' room.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.01,1:46:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someone stole it and put it in an envelope and handed it to Maria, just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.69,1:46:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.03,1:46:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.27,1:47:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I took the key out of Maria's envelope and opened this door,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.92,1:47:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it was definitely locked.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.92,1:47:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But this key was in the envelope and in Maria's care, right?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.54,1:47:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was before noon yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.84,1:47:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the culprit open the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.48,1:47:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.72,1:47:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Another annoying closed room again?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.83,1:47:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, if it was a human, what trick could they have used to defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.91,1:47:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like the closed rooms last time. Not enough information! It's impossible to reason like this!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.03,1:47:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do this, I shall add a new rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.64,1:47:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.54,1:47:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.20,1:47:47.50,RedText,,0,0,0,,When I speak the truth, I will use red.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.27,1:47:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.91,1:47:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You always keep running away by repeating "lack of information" and "uncertain basis".
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.42,1:48:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I want to give you the information and basis you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.40,1:48:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.39,1:48:06.11,RedText,,0,0,0,,Everything I speak in red is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.48,1:48:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely no need to doubt it!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.65,1:48:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.17,1:48:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In a game, the rules are sacred! Those who take that lightly are not qualified to play!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.02,1:48:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll accept that rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.86,1:48:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.90,1:48:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and the rest used a hidden door to enter the chapel, or were carried in through it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.11,1:48:30.50,RedText,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether they were alive or dead, the six definitely enter through the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.80,1:48:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.53,1:48:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I will supplement the rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.62,1:48:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When I speak the truth, I will use red.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.78,1:48:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I do not bear the responsibility of establishing that by showing proof
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.87,1:48:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything said in red is simply the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.73,1:48:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is simple. I carried out all of the crimes with magic. That makes anything possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.67,1:48:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unfair game.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.30,1:48:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So shall we resume once more? How will you defeat this closed room?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.93,1:49:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit secretly made a duplicate key.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.92,1:49:04.41,RedText,,0,0,0,,Only one key to the chapel exists!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.65,1:49:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit made something other than a legitimate key and opened the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.94,1:49:11.35,RedText,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to unlock the lock to the chapel without the chapel's key!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.62,1:49:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some kind of trick with the door. Even while it is locked, there was some way to pass through it
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.23,1:49:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the intelligence of humans, Battler?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.20,1:49:21.08,RedText,,0,0,0,,When the door to the chapel is locked, it prevents any and all methods of entry or exit!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.18,1:49:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.49,1:49:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Think, don't give up! How can I not get checkmated by the witch?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.43,1:49:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate...?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.01,1:49:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When considering something, the closer you get to the very, very end, the easier it becomes to anticipate.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.17,1:49:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the opponent has only one move left,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.77,1:49:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Flip the chessboard around!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.02,1:49:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to get into the chapel is through that door, and there's only one key.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.22,1:49:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But the important thing is whether that key was really in Maria's possession since noon yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.67,1:50:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Maria got the envelope from you yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.62,1:50:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if the key in the envelope is a fake...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.68,1:50:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.90,1:50:13.08,RedText,,0,0,0,,This morning, Rosa definitely took an envelope of Maria's handbag,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.08,1:50:16.87,RedText,,0,0,0,,and from that obtained the genuine key to the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.98,1:50:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.62,1:50:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Until Aunt Rosa took out the envelope, that envelope was completely under Maria's supervision."
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.13,1:50:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn of the Golden Witch! Show me how you defeat that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.71,1:50:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.58,1:50:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Until Aunt Rosa took out the envelope, no one was able to touch Maria's handbag."
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.22,1:50:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse this, and I won't explain why.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.16,1:50:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me explain for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.09,1:50:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you entrusted Maria with the key, some time between then and this morning
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.76,1:50:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit stole the envelope from Maria's handbag. They locked the chapel with the key.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.46,1:50:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And put the key back in the envelope sealed it with wax once more, and returned it to Maria's handbag.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.19,1:50:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for magic! This is a closed room trick possible for humans!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.17,1:51:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up! I resign! Just once, on this one board, I will give up!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.50,1:51:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you really are naive.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.38,1:51:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.18,1:51:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still not understand? As long as you continue to deny my existence, you will eventually be forced to suspect those relatives.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.84,1:51:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You will certainly accept my existence!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.15,1:51:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the culprit is still on this island.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.39,1:51:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.99,1:51:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.45,1:51:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting aside whether the culprit is that mysterious guest of honor or not, it's still very unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.22,1:51:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, we've been suspecting that vistor who called herself Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.76,1:51:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the possiblity that she's a victim whose body still hasn't been found.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.20,1:51:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice-sama was not in her room.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.66,1:51:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Jessica?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.84,1:51:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica is currently being looked after by Kanon-san.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.84,1:51:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably meet up with them soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.26,1:52:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is telling us to solve the riddle of the epitaph, I wonder if they are planning to snatch away the gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.63,1:52:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice hasn't said a thing about wanting gold.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.56,1:52:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice is just asking whether everyone can solve the riddle of the epitaph or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.77,1:52:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.41,1:52:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa... what is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.46,1:52:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This belong to Father. I borrowed it specially.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.77,1:52:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Grandfather okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.85,1:52:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine. He said that he won't leave his room, so he's probably safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.81,1:52:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we should do all we can to gather in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.94,1:52:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I also think that is good!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.03,1:52:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Maybe it would be good to call Milady here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.79,1:52:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go with a couple people!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.09,1:52:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.70,1:52:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go together. This is a "wolves and sheep puzzle".
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.20,1:52:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.70,1:52:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Genji, you lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.50,1:52:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.33,1:52:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We all move together to keep the sheep from being attacked by wolves.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.15,1:53:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a wolf in sheep clothing among us...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.10,1:53:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No... There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.10,1:53:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.67,1:53:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.57,1:53:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Another magic circle?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.00,1:53:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first magic circle of the moon. It has the power to open the closed door.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.87,1:53:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.20,1:53:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.47,1:53:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is locked...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.00,1:53:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice. Open it with the master key.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.04,1:53:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica-sama!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.76,1:53:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica!!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.88,1:53:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Jessica even?!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.98,1:53:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.68,1:53:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... horrible. Not much time has passed since she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.84,1:53:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Kanon-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.88,1:53:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.94,1:53:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out if there is anyone hiding in the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.18,1:53:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is this key? If anyone knows, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.61,1:53:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It is probably the key to Milady's room.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.69,1:53:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The only key that can open this door is this one and the servants' master keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.20,1:53:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.00,1:53:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How many master keys are there?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.92,1:54:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We servants each hold one master key. There are no additional ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:07.05,1:54:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second... In the last game, I thought we said there were extra master keys?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.39,1:54:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Having several master keys whose locations are unknown is quite troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.72,1:54:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have altered the setup.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.32,1:54:22.26,RedText,,0,0,0,,The only master keys are the ones held by the servants, one key each.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.86,1:54:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Messing with me like this...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.83,1:54:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what is your next move?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.53,1:54:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You will see, if you listen to Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.96,1:54:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I've sorted out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.80,1:54:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.00,1:54:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, Jessica-chan's key is here. That means it was impossible for this room to be locked with anything but the master keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.24,1:54:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean you are suspecting us, the servants?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.51,1:54:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too harsh!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.30,1:54:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a simple process of elimination.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.61,1:55:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that would make the most suspicious person the one who's missing right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.67,1:55:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you don't mean Kanon-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.94,1:55:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Beatrice is the culprit, there is also the possiblity that he is an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.80,1:55:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.51,1:55:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be careless, even if Kanon shows up safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.54,1:55:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...Unless he can be proven innocent.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.82,1:55:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume that the culprit who killed Jessica-chan is Kanon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.85,1:55:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Why are they treating Kanon-kun like the culprit, just because there's no corpse?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.48,1:55:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, because I was finally able to be of use to Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.30,1:55:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this. Someone...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.00,1:55:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please defend Kanon-kun's honor!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.11,1:55:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.83,1:55:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all useless.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.23,1:55:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-sama.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.43,1:55:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find evidence that Kanon-kun isn't the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.36,1:55:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Battler-kun, which of the other servants do you suspect?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.26,1:56:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just the servants. No one in our family is going to kill because of a pile of money!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.64,1:56:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how are you going to prove that Kanon is not the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.47,1:56:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.74,1:56:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun was not holding a master key.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.80,1:56:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.70,1:56:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda-san. You and Kanon chased after Jessica to the VIP room, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.50,1:56:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.97,1:56:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.67,1:56:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose key was used to unlock the VIP room at that time?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.97,1:56:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kanon-san's.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.28,1:56:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.15,1:56:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, if Jessica-chan didn't give that key back to Kanon-kun...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.21,1:56:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nanjo, would you mind checking for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.60,1:56:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.41,1:56:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt, this is the master key.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.51,1:56:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Kanon-kun could not have locked this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.81,1:56:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It does seem that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.28,1:56:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as long as we cannot find Kanon-kun. That doesn't change the fact that he is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.05,1:56:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop this, Aunt Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.15,1:56:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.28,1:57:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be a little hard to keep people from suspecting each other in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.90,1:57:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.94,1:57:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not permit accusations without evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.54,1:57:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to accuse someone of being guilty, prepare some perfect evidence!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.27,1:57:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, well done. Not a bad job.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.14,1:57:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You splendidly proved that Kanon could not have locked this door.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.50,1:57:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who locked the door?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.04,1:57:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.34,1:57:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I would like to verify what you mean by "this room is a closed room."
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.17,1:57:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.95,1:57:44.59,RedText,,0,0,0,,There are absolutely no types of hidden doors. This door is the only way in or out.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.69,1:57:53.32,RedText,,0,0,0,,The only way to lock this door is with Jessica's single key or the master keys, only one of which is held by each servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.45,1:57:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Repetition requested. "Kanon-kun was killed in this room".
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.85,1:57:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmhm.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.50,1:57:59.30,RedText,,0,0,0,,Kanon was killed in this room.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.33,1:58:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, repetition requested.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.97,1:58:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kanon-kun's corpse is in this room."
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.04,1:58:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse. I can't repeat it. Because I erased the corpse with magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.85,1:58:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Repetition requested. "The last time it was locked was with a master key".
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.08,1:58:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I also refuse that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.76,1:58:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This refusing thing is really vague.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.53,1:58:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when discussing the lock to the chapel, you completely turned the tables on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.29,1:58:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, speaking of the chapel, it's the same here as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.85,1:58:27.80,RedText,,0,0,0,,When locked, entry is not possible by any means.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.80,1:58:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.69,1:58:33.93,RedText,,0,0,0,,No trick could have the effect of locking the door from the outside without using a key.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.75,1:58:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stop using the red when I don't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.37,1:58:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's back up!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.00,1:58:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My purpose is to figure out how these crimes were committed by the 19th person, the human visitor,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.03,1:58:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't have to suspect anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.80,1:58:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a foolish man.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.40,1:58:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This room wasn't originally a closed room.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.81,1:58:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, there are six keys that can open the lock.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.47,1:59:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also several people with these keys, so you can suspect them as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.00,1:59:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.70,1:59:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But you deliberately denied all of this and created a closed room of your own.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.45,1:59:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.85,1:59:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a closed room made from the contradictions in your own thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.71,1:59:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. As long as I suspect relatives, everything's fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.85,1:59:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.26,1:59:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I definitely can't accept the existence of a witch!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.66,1:59:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The only answer I can give now is...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.26,1:59:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...I resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.98,1:59:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.54,1:59:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up. I was able to prove that Kanon-kun couldn't have locked this door.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.05,2:00:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I couldn't figure out who killed Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.04,2:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But Battler-sama, for Kanon-kun's sake—
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.00,2:00:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And that also means being suspicious of other people.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.16,2:00:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.08,2:00:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa, sorry. It's not like I wanted to resist you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.76,2:00:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. I was also a little rash. Let's make up.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.08,2:00:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We are mutually-dependent sheep, but because I deny the witch...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.77,2:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It means acknowledging there are wolves among us at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.50,2:00:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.18,2:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.63,2:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be right back from the servants' room as soon as I have the essentials ready for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.87,2:01:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have asked Doctor Nanjo to leave as well.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.30,2:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to discuss something amongst the relatives.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.72,2:01:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.15,2:01:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we will take our leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.04,2:01:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa, can I go with them?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.09,2:01:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.75,2:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone here is a member of the Ushiromiya family.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.46,2:01:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say that you have chased out all the "wolves"?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.95,2:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun, you are a quick thinker.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.21,2:01:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolves?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.42,2:01:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa has decided that the servants are wolves of the "wolves and sheep puzzle,"
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.64,2:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which means treating them like accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.50,2:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it be that simple?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.58,2:01:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of whether Beatrice is the real culprit or not.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.14,2:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there are multiple conspirators.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.20,2:02:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The first murder where Nii-san and the rest were killed — do you think a single person could have pulled that off?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.08,2:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if the servants were the culprits, why would they lock the door after killing Jessica?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.53,2:02:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In doing so, it'd be inevitable that they'd be suspected since they hold the master keys.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.86,2:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can lock the door to that room without the master key, that's another matter.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.26,2:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.67,2:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole uproar in Jessica's room about Kanon-kun being the culprit was to test the reactions of the servants?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.35,2:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, it made me even more suspicious of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.35,2:02:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely a wolf among the servants.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.72,2:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then isn't Shannon in danger right?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.19,2:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon-chan went with Genji-san to see Father earlier.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.22,2:02:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She was supposedly isolated then, but she wasn't killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.95,2:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Genji-san isn't a wolf either, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.60,2:02:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong. It's because they're both wolves.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.03,2:02:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon isn't that kind of person who would take part in such a wicked crime! Please take back what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.90,2:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I don't think I deserve any praise right now!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.48,2:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm a mother! Maria's mother. And now, to both of you. So, I cannot let my guard down!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.26,2:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Always stay where I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.02,2:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I... will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.90,2:03:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're at it, you'll be observing us to make sure we are not wolves.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.22,2:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Aunt Rosa? Can you prove you're not a "wolf"?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:35.92,2:03:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.53,2:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With this.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.00,2:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think about it, if I were the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.94,2:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the servants are gone, would I miss this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.21,2:03:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a crude theory, but it does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.07,2:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you have to understand that I'm trying to protect you from this malicious culprit.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.53,2:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For that purpose, I'd become a demon.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.83,2:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.10,2:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, is the Master okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.20,2:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's safe in his study.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:26.86,2:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a fully equipped refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.10,2:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to us now?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.27,2:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Rosa-sama?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.72,2:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Genji-san.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.44,2:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.70,2:04:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanjo and the women, stand back.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.85,2:04:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-kun? Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.35,2:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.45,2:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We must inform Rosa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.28,2:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.12,2:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... tell Rosa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:57.02,2:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- what do you mean, Kanon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.45,2:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama came...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.00,2:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...to Milady...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.00,2:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.20,2:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.65,2:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Rosa...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.70,2:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you... I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.25,2:05:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon-san!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.05,2:05:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rosa-sama is the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.15,2:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what will happen to Battler-sama and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.65,2:05:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But, wouldn't it be better if we didn't provoke them too much...?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.70,2:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'll massacre us all.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.42,2:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to have the Master's wealth all to herself, she told me clearly.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.35,2:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,K- Kanon, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.58,2:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? It isn't a serious wound.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.30,2:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.22,2:05:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanon-san, stop it!!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.42,2:05:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, not a serious wound.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.83,2:05:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san. Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.30,2:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to look for something.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.99,2:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.13,2:06:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really... Kanon-kun?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.25,2:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.84,2:06:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a handkerchief with a spider's web stucked onto it.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.96,2:06:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're Kanon-kun, then you should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.06,2:06:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the spider is your natural enemy,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.40,2:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumasawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.50,2:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You senile old furniture!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.00,2:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.90,2:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Genji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.20,2:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.54,2:06:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let... Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.50,2:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that thing near me!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.00,2:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aahhhhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.37,2:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda, you're not hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.70,2:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What... did we see?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.30,2:06:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.20,2:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon-chan and the others told us what they saw
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.25,2:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't believe that it was the truth.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.48,2:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a B-rated horror movie.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.60,2:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But they said it did happen, that they saw it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.20,2:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to the servant room together dubiously.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.60,2:07:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, after unlocking the door again,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.95,2:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.80,2:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.77,2:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The two bodies... aren't here!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.89,2:07:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as Jessica's room? They've disappeared from inside a closed room again?!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.95,2:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe us, Rosa-sama! We definitely...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.25,2:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.02,2:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a message from the person who hid the body.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.22,2:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the one from the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.70,2:07:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,People of the Ushiromiya family.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.80,2:08:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if your attempts at solving the epitaph have gotten far.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.80,2:08:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Solving the epitaph is the single method by which you can stop me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.50,2:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not be able to stop me, or this ritual, by way or any other method of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.20,2:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you all to not mistake your goal.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.86,2:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting to search for me is useless.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.57,2:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting to escape from me is useless.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:17.44,2:08:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting to deny me is useless.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.22,2:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice the Golden.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.77,2:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.04,2:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,P.S: The remains of the two have been borrowed for the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.44,2:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return them later, so please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.95,2:08:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, since these keys belong to all of you, I'm returning them.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.09,2:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Kanon's and Kumasawa's master keys.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:45.50,2:08:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, damn it...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.67,2:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can only suspect the servants holding keys again?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.56,2:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't say it in red, alright?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.36,2:08:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what about the original keys to the servant room?!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.65,2:09:02.74,RedText,,0,0,0,,Those are kept in the key box in center of the servant room.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.94,2:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than that, the conditions have not changed.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.17,2:09:10.68,RedText,,0,0,0,,Entry or exit is impossible except for the single door and single window.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.69,2:09:13.43,RedText,,0,0,0,,And those were both locked.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.43,2:09:18.42,RedText,,0,0,0,,The door and the windows do not permit any kind of entry or exit when they are locked.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.80,2:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.81,2:09:24.34,RedText,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to unlock the door without a key to the servant room or the master key.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.33,2:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, it's all useless.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.30,2:09:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Think. Think!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.70,2:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Flip the chessboard around.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.54,2:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry the corpses, leave the letter, and lock the door, without relying on a hidden door.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.40,2:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.65,2:09:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.83,2:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Beato, before my repetition request.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.26,2:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to first check the definition of what you mean by hidden doors.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.75,2:10:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you thought of?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.84,2:10:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A hidden door refers to an entrance or exit that cannot be recognized by those who do not know of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:06.71,2:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if it doesn't get to the outside of the room, it's not a hidden door.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.83,2:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoh... Here it comes
Dialogue: 0,2:10:14.07,2:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept thinking that it was something that let the culprit escape the closed room.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.00,2:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this was not the case.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.45,2:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the culprit couldn't escape the closed room!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.50,2:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if there were, for example, something like a "hidden shelf" or a "secret closet," they wouldn't be defined as "hidden doors."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.41,2:10:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The third person in Jessica's room was hiding here, waiting for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.82,2:10:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this very moment,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.20,2:10:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is still hiding in the servant room!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.19,2:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Repetition requested! "There is no one in this room other than us."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.10,2:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By us, I mean me, George-aniki, Maria, Aunt Rosa, Genji-san, Gohda-san, and Shannon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.62,2:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse, then I will keep going.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.56,2:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat this!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.75,2:10:57.30,RedText,,0,0,0,,There is no one in this room other than your group.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.53,2:11:03.96,RedText,,0,0,0,,"Your group" refers to Battler, George, Maria, Rosa, Genji, Gohda, and Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.50,2:11:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.00,2:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to Jessica's room.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.00,2:11:10.86,RedText,,0,0,0,,When Jessica's corpse was discovered, in Jessica's room
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.86,2:11:16.71,RedText,,0,0,0,,only Battler, George, Maria, Rosa, Genji, Gohda, Shannon, Kumasawa, and Nanjo were there.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.70,2:11:20.11,RedText,,0,0,0,,This also includes the corpse of Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.42,2:11:28.92,RedText,,0,0,0,,Therefore, both in the case of Jessica's room and the case in this servants' room, no humans exist that you were not aware of. No one is hiding.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.31,2:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say more.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:30.89,2:11:35.32,RedText,,0,0,0,,No method exists by which the door can be locked from the outside without using a key.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.32,2:11:39.65,RedText,,0,0,0,,And there's no method that exists to lock a window from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.88,2:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I'm at it,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.68,2:11:43.50,RedText,,0,0,0,,You are incompetent!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.50,2:11:49.19,RedText,,0,0,0,,Hihihihihihihihihihihihihihihihihi!!
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.20,2:11:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The light... was swallowed up by the deep red sea...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.32,2:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's clear. There's no more room for doubt.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.70,2:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.70,2:12:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two that you kept saying were dead aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.75,2:12:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we have the letter from Beatrice, where she was kind enough to confess that she carried the corpses off.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.30,2:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this farce!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:17.01,2:12:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,F- farce, you say, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.81,2:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we cannot find the corpses, there's no reason we should accept that those two were killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.20,2:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment, this is-
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.35,2:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nanjo and Kumasawa-san are still alive!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.85,2:12:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They made it seem like they were killed, and are hiding somewhere in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:32.20,2:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama!!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.30,2:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All the servants of the Ushiromiya swear that nothing of the sort happened!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.50,2:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.20,2:12:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can't find their corpses, there is no way to deny the possibility that you are wolves!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.00,2:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You and you!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.50,2:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you were bought off by blinding gold!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.50,2:12:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama, even we...!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.10,2:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be silent!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:52.20,2:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that you would repay a ten-year long debt of gratitude with betrayal!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.72,2:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Rosa!
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.08,2:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you... go that far?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.92,2:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:10.50,2:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa-sama is acting in a state of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:14.56,2:13:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are furniture that serves the Ushiromiya family...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:20.19,2:13:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this key was entrusted to me as a proof of trust.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.06,2:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If that has been lost, I think it is only natural that I return it.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.06,2:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...You two.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.80,2:13:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, give me that handbag.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.10,2:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu — ...
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.90,2:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are holding all five of the keys. Are you satisfied now, Aunt Rosa?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.40,2:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.65,2:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't trust anyone, I can at least trust myself!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:05.60,2:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... I don't have to suspect anyone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.60,2:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice can open doors with magic.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:14.60,2:14:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who carries the keys!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.70,2:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I always tell you to stop laughing like that?!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.30,2:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Battler-kun?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.00,2:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop already...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.80,2:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria was right.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:39.00,2:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.70,2:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.00,2:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sorry for doubting you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.80,2:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because I don't believe in witches.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.45,2:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why,
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.75,2:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in so much pain...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.71,2:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this sad.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.10,2:15:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-san...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.60,2:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to suspect anyone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:10.70,2:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, Battler!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.23,2:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice 'exists', and because Battler believed in Beato, he will surely be invited to the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.83,2:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's solve the riddle of the epitaph together with Maria.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.60,2:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Beato has been saying it from the beginning, that she wants to play and solve the epitaph.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:29.50,2:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.30,2:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:36.90,2:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.60,2:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...should have just believed from the start.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:46.30,2:15:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we have returned the master keys, our loyalty will not change
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.10,2:15:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are an admirable man.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:56.70,2:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When the typhoon passes, if the cries of the seagulls return to this island again...
Dialogue: 0,2:16:03.94,2:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...we will be able to trust each other again.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.91,2:16:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it will be my greatest joy.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.35,2:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... going with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:12.84,2:16:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.90,2:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun, stay with Aunt Rosa in the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:17.39,2:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I... want to stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:21.00,2:16:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —! Maria will protect Battler.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.00,2:16:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck Maria-chan!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:26.70,2:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then with that, we will be off. If you will excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:50.00,2:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't trust them at all,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:52.10,2:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,damn furniture.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.93,2:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...What?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:55.85,2:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only five master keys? They must still be hiding more.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.70,2:17:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we could trust them just because they pulled keys out of their pockets.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:04.89,2:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.90,2:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They ended up doing this for us!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:07.40,2:17:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Devil's proof!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:09.70,2:17:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can show that there are five master keys by glancing at them.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.57,2:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you can't prove that no more than five exist!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.30,2:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a demon or a witch could prove something like that!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.20,2:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, please, Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:34.70,2:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself right now and tell them that there's no more than five keys, and there's no need to suspect anyone!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:43.40,2:17:48.40,RedText,,0,0,0,,There are only five master keys. There are only five master keys.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:49.00,2:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? No matter what I say, it won't reach Rosa's ears.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.93,2:18:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that some people still exist that deny me, so she can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:02.50,2:18:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept it, you exist, you exist, you definitely exist!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:07.10,2:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then show me with your actions!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:08.90,2:18:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your clothes and become completely naked,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:12.05,2:18:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and use your tongue to lick my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:15.52,2:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do, I'll appear and say it in red!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.81,2:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushiromiya Battleeeeeeeer!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:30.84,2:18:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:35.31,2:18:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all because I broke the mirror, that it became the power to revive Beatrice-sama
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.46,2:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon, you don't have to bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.17,2:18:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's true,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:45.30,2:18:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we seal Beatrice-sama with a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.01,2:18:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary mirrors probably won't...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:51.22,2:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that Madam keeps a spirit mirror as a charm.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.33,2:18:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Natsuhi?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:58.63,2:19:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that it is a mirror that held a very strong magic repelling power, of high pedigree?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.94,2:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard Aunt Natsuhi came from a family of Shinto priests.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.72,2:19:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can really resist Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:07.65,2:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard Madam say that she keeps it safe in a treasure box.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.19,2:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. There's nothing else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.37,2:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It is worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.40,2:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the door to Madam's room is locked.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.01,2:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, Aunt Natsuhi should have been walking around with that key.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.41,2:19:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can break the windows of the chapel and get in.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:22.52,2:19:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.17,2:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:28.97,2:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the Master can call for me at any time, I must remain here.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:33.84,2:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the duty of the Ushiromiya family's servant.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.42,2:19:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.15,2:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:57.14,2:20:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the letter suggested, Maria and I started to challenge the riddle of the epitaph.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.23,2:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On the first twilight, sacrifice the six chosen by the key.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:09.32,2:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On the second twilight, those who remain shall tear apart the two who are close.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.12,2:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously this hinted at the murders that have already taken place.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.45,2:20:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... On the fourth twilight, gouge the head and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:25.05,2:20:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On the fifth twilight, gouge the chest and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.05,2:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the sixth twilight, gouge the stomach and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.80,2:20:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On the seventh twilight, gouge the knee and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:33.60,2:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On the eighth twilight, gouge the leg and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.80,2:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we assume that Doctor Nanjo and Kumasawa were both sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,2:20:43.13,2:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be three more.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.13,2:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —. Baa-ttaa-leeeer!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:50.56,2:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it again, that Beatrice said she would do if we solve this riddle?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.02,2:20:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If the epitaph is solved, the ceremony is over, and no one else is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.04,2:21:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Committing these serial murders,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.31,2:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and deliberately telling us the conditions for her own defeat?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.54,2:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like she doesn't care whether she wins or loses.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.40,2:21:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:31.94,2:21:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is painful no matter how many times I see it.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:34.41,2:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.44,2:21:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it, the key to Madam's room.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.40,2:21:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon-san!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:47.23,2:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful reception for the host of the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.00,2:21:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the exact three people I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.89,2:22:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it, but this box is locked.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.81,2:22:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pry it open quickly, George-sama.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.70,2:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon-san!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:27.23,2:22:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.59,2:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you see that? Your life flashing before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:41.38,2:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gohda.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.64,2:22:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The roulette has chosen you and George.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:47.58,2:22:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shannon, you wanted to be embraced by your beloved, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:52.09,2:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You want him to teach you a woman's pleasure, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.27,2:23:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your regret is hanging from your mouth. I can see it dribbling from corner of your lips.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.29,2:23:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.22,2:23:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One step too late.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.74,2:23:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-shannon.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:13.45,2:23:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,George stay there. Don't move. I don't want to shift the central axis.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:16.93,2:23:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent power, furniture!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:19.96,2:23:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not furniture and right now I think you're very pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.15,2:23:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:25.78,2:23:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,George-san and I have sworn our love to each other, our eternal vows were completed!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:30.63,2:23:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:33.57,2:23:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Stop talking you damn furniture, you trash scrap of furniture!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.37,2:23:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.47,2:23:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:52.55,2:23:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for fighting for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:56.96,2:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.00,2:24:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,George-san, in the end...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:02.17,2:24:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me hear you say "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,2:24:06.68,2:24:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sayo.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:09.76,2:24:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always...
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.40,2:24:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:38.73,2:24:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Genji.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.73,2:24:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it right there.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.80,2:24:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The bodies of Doctor Nanjo and Kumasawa were found in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:49.74,2:24:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On the seventh twilight, gouge the knee and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:55.20,2:25:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On the eighth twilight, gouge the leg and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:01.95,2:25:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you described, they both have wounds on their necks.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:05.87,2:25:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what is this, a stake?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:08.27,2:25:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:11.13,2:25:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Knees and leg, this is the seventh and eighth twilight of the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:15.35,2:25:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that means...!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.90,2:25:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nanjo and them were killed in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:26.69,2:25:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it is already,
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.22,2:25:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On the fifth twilight, gouge the chest and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.88,2:25:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On the sixth twilight, gouge the stomach and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.23,2:25:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.34,2:25:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:53.41,2:25:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.26,2:25:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:57.92,2:25:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest and... stomach...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:01.27,2:26:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,2:26:02.24,2:26:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On the fourth twilight, gouge the head and kill.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.85,2:26:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun, you mustn't touch anything until the police arrive!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:16.44,2:26:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:19.57,2:26:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the ninth twilight again?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.00,2:26:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,On the ninth twilight, the witch shall revive, and none shall be left alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.16,2:26:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:33.86,2:26:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to die after this?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:39.41,2:26:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,On the tenth twilight, the journey shall end, you will arrive at the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.06,2:26:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The witch shall praise the wise and bestow four treasures.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:51.17,2:26:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One shall be all the gold from the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.95,2:26:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One shall be the resurrection of all the dead souls.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:59.12,2:27:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One shall be the resurrection of the love that was lost.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:03.57,2:27:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One shall be to put the witch to sleep for all time.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:21.37,2:27:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all of this, you're still leaving Genji to be alone?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.44,2:27:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When did this..?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:37.78,2:27:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you made more progress with the epitaph?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.16,2:27:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is quickly running out
Dialogue: 0,2:27:42.33,2:27:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The ninth twilight is about to begin
Dialogue: 0,2:27:45.17,2:27:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:47.14,2:27:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when it got here.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:48.41,2:27:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:53.35,2:27:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.79,2:27:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have concluded that you are a "wolf".
Dialogue: 0,2:27:58.21,2:27:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:59.18,2:28:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When I entered this room, that letter wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.77,2:28:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you could have put the letter there.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:04.80,2:28:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suspecting me because of that? My dad and family were all killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.99,2:28:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:10.08,2:28:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you could have received a large sum of money,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:13.21,2:28:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would sell their own flesh and blood parents for this reason?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:15.84,2:28:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're not the real Ushiromiya Battler.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:20.23,2:28:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's with this ridiculous thinking!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:23.35,2:28:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you for six years.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.75,2:28:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you could be a stranger who's trying to swindle the Ushiromiya family's fortune!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.86,2:28:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:44.11,2:28:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 0,2:28:46.12,2:28:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be suspecting you!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.93,2:28:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.67,2:28:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be proving it to me!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:51.01,2:28:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were a wolf, I would have shot you with this gun.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:53.67,2:28:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.22,2:29:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of relatives, six of them died. Why are you the only one alive?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.05,2:29:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one reason
Dialogue: 0,2:29:05.47,2:29:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you killed Dad and them.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:08.71,2:29:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The witch did it, it is neither of your fault, it's nobody's fault.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.94,2:29:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.84,2:29:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the witch's doing.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.69,2:29:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all a crime Beatrice committed with magic.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.95,2:29:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry up and show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.47,2:29:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And confess to us that everything was your doing.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:48.16,2:29:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you won!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.03,2:29:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You do exist!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:54.92,2:29:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:00.21,2:30:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:25.62,2:30:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice, if I can see your smiling face one more time, I don't need anything else
Dialogue: 0,2:30:33.48,2:30:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me say a word of apology.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:39.05,2:30:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinzo, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:41.38,2:30:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just say something simpler?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:46.14,2:30:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:52.07,2:30:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.54,2:30:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.88,2:31:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! The door's not locked at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:28.97,2:31:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.14,2:31:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to carry out my last rites?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:35.03,2:31:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony has been completed by the eighth twilight.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.30,2:31:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it should be alright to tell you everything now.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:43.15,2:31:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:44.95,2:31:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall guide you to the master's study.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:59.01,2:32:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, Battler-sama you will probably see things that are incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:03.93,2:32:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.43,2:32:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:20.19,2:32:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I counter this? I've thought for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:27.19,2:32:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun, so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:30.56,2:32:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this？
Dialogue: 0,2:32:32.76,2:32:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it, Ushiromiya Battler.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:34.36,2:32:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you called my name many times, I came to allow you to ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:41.46,2:32:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a ton of things I want to ask!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:43.46,2:32:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is going on on this island and why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:47.96,2:32:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And about the closed rooms!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:49.46,2:32:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened in the chapel?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:50.49,2:32:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Jessica's room?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:51.46,2:32:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Aunt Natsuhi's room?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:52.82,2:32:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the servant's room?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:53.82,2:32:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the parlor?!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:55.82,2:32:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:57.29,2:32:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:58.99,2:33:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call me here?!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:00.89,2:33:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. However, I have one condition.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:06.95,2:33:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...What is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:08.31,2:33:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After listening to everything, if you are able to accept my existence,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:13.61,2:33:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel down and kiss my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.44,2:33:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you here to make you surrender.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:23.20,2:33:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure! I'll kiss you or do whatever else for you!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:28.60,2:33:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, let's start with what a witch is!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:52.88,2:33:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the witch began to tell of everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:57.90,2:34:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She started providing answers to all of Battler's questions.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.90,2:34:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was logical.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:03.75,2:34:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything made sense.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:05.86,2:34:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So Battler had no choice but to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:10.38,2:34:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The witch truly did "exist".
Dialogue: 0,2:34:14.95,2:34:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is a tale that doesn't need to be told.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:20.27,2:34:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After toppling the king and resigning, all that remains is to reflect on one's moves.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:26.29,2:34:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And set the pieces up once more.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:31.00,2:34:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is the Golden Witch, Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:36.52,2:34:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When the seagulls cried,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.61,2:34:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000ff}none{\c&Hffffff} were left alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:54.99,2:34:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself! I know you're there, Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:14.39,2:35:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just this one piece...
Dialogue: 0,2:35:20.29,2:35:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The door to the Golden Land is about to open.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:24.29,2:35:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:26.49,2:35:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, show yourself, Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:37.52,2:35:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:39.86,2:35:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:42.69,2:35:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:45.86,2:35:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight marks the revival of our Golden Witch.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:50.74,2:35:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice will now make her entrance.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:06.55,2:36:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for gathering tonight for the me!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:09.64,2:36:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time for me to open the gate of the Golden Land.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:20.38,2:36:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice, now is the time to send me to the Golden Land!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:32.27,2:36:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink, eat, sing, dance, laugh, intimidate, assault, return.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:42.56,2:36:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down on your knees to pay your respects.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:44.77,2:36:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear to give all flesh and blood to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:50.18,2:36:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even worthy to be my furniture.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:53.99,2:37:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is entertaining the guests the most you can do now?
Dialogue: 0,2:37:19.97,2:37:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, quickly, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:22.21,2:37:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:23.61,2:37:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.32,2:37:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:31.33,2:37:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Try laying one finger on Maria, I dare you.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:33.80,2:37:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you just how lukewarm the hell you came from is!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:39.31,2:37:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:45.98,2:37:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Load the bullets in, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:47.28,2:37:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:49.84,2:37:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you... what my golden dream looks like!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:56.17,2:37:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, the bullets are loaded.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:57.69,2:37:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job! Stay next to me!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:14.11,2:38:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:16.00,2:38:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:17.10,2:38:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:23.61,2:38:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what has my life been anyway?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:27.30,2:38:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost all my money,
Dialogue: 0,2:38:29.18,2:38:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was looked down on by my siblings,
Dialogue: 0,2:38:32.42,2:38:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I even put Maria in danger.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:37.85,2:38:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:39.83,2:38:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,2:38:41.30,2:38:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama just remembered something she needs to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:43.59,2:38:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead without me!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:45.08,2:38:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no no no no no!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:48.17,2:38:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay with you, I don't want Mama to die!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:52.88,2:38:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll say you want to stay with me, even though I am such a bad Mama?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:57.90,2:39:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay with Mama, I want to stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:01.95,2:39:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I always make it look like I put you first, but I always put you off.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:08.06,2:39:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I am such a bad Mama?!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:11.08,2:39:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's only one Mama in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:16.25,2:39:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be happy as long as the one Mama in the world is with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:23.77,2:39:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,2:39:28.30,2:39:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need any gold! I should have just held your hand!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:39.30,2:39:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:42.60,2:39:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu —!
Dialogue: 0,2:39:52.00,2:39:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever wants to eat the bullets Maria chambered for me...
Dialogue: 0,2:39:57.60,2:39:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:13.80,2:40:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:20.20,2:40:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My body feels heavy...
Dialogue: 0,2:40:24.80,2:40:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My head feels dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:28.94,2:40:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can grant you whatever it is that you desire. Think of it as a reward for your good luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:36.91,2:40:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:38.99,2:40:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:42.95,2:40:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Golden Witch. I would have no problem bestowing you a mountain of gold.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:49.00,2:40:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems that this wouldn't satisfy you.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:52.87,2:40:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosa!
Dialogue: 0,2:40:55.43,2:40:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:59.40,2:41:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:00.10,2:41:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots shouldn't interrupt, Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:03.14,2:41:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:04.10,2:41:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, right? After all, it's Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:07.35,2:41:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:08.58,2:41:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate my brothers and sisters!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:13.32,2:41:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, your pain is a fate you have shouldered from the time you were born.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:20.07,2:41:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall give you the joy of having your days of suffering rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:25.12,2:41:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Food accounts for much of a human's pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:28.63,2:41:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we hold a gourmet banquet that will continue until the pain in your heart is healed?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:31.30,2:41:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:32.27,2:41:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The apéritif is a cocktail. If I had to give it a name, it'd be called a Bloody-Krauss.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:42.00,2:41:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it delicious? It's been dyed with golden drops of blood squeezed out of your brother, Krauss, after placing him in a compressor.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:50.35,2:41:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:52.83,2:41:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,2:41:55.13,2:41:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Forked-tongued salad made from seasonal vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:58.95,2:42:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made with Eva's tongue, which you always wished you could bite off one day.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:03.89,2:42:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:07.47,2:42:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is a sea bass pie wrapped in the skin of Rudolf's face.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:11.04,2:42:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:12.65,2:42:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOO!!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:13.80,2:42:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thrilled, aren't you, Ushiromiya Rosa? Don't pretend like you don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:18.96,2:42:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:20.53,2:42:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I planned to keep the dessert a secret to surprise you,
Dialogue: 0,2:42:24.53,2:42:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I suppose I'll reveal it. Perhaps revealing it now will give you the incentive to finish the main course.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:31.75,2:42:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's oven-baked Maria and apples. Eat that, and you will be freed from everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:39.01,2:42:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:40.67,2:42:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, was Maria a burden?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:45.07,2:42:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a burden, not a burden!
Dialogue: 0,2:42:47.30,2:42:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever Mama went to stay over with a man, I would get lonely and make a mess of my room.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.35,2:42:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go to search for Mama by myself, I get lost...
Dialogue: 0,2:42:56.59,2:43:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm like this... I'm a burden to Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:02.01,2:43:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being born!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:03.68,2:43:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:04.48,2:43:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll become delicious oven-baked apples for Mama's sake.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:07.97,2:43:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, will mom feel really good for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:11.66,2:43:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you eat me, you'll think I am delicious!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:14.42,2:43:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:15.29,2:43:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:17.75,2:43:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Maria, I don't want this! No!!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:21.28,2:43:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will have you acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:24.16,2:43:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Acknowledge the fact that I'm a witch.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:28.03,2:43:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I acknowledge it... I acknowledge that Beatrice is a witch.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:31.70,2:43:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So give Maria back to me!!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:35.06,2:43:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got you to acknowledge it! Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:38.86,2:43:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:41.48,2:43:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take Maria away! Prepare a delicious oven roast for Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:45.80,2:43:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOO!!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:48.43,2:43:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:50.20,2:43:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you slice up those cow tits of yours and make me a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:04.32,2:44:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler?! You bastard... You should have already surrendered down to your very soul!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:09.80,2:44:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, but while I was listening to that gross recipe, I started to get a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:16.00,2:44:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I started craving a whole roast witch!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:18.50,2:44:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:19.40,2:44:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:20.82,2:44:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ten years too early for you to talk about having someone eat you up. But in ten years, you'd better say that to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:25.80,2:44:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:26.60,2:44:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uu, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:28.53,2:44:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Battler-kun...
Dialogue: 0,2:44:30.34,2:44:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Aunt Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:32.76,2:44:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a one-on-one fight between me and this woman.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:37.30,2:44:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,2:44:40.20,2:44:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...cannot surrender!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:46.30,2:44:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How amusing! I wouldn't have you any other way, Ushiromiya Battler!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:51.50,2:44:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, just try to deny me!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:55.45,2:44:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make you surrender over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,2:44:59.38,2:45:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:02.30,2:45:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 0,2:45:02.70,2:45:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all
Dialogue: 0,2:45:03.30,2:45:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all useless!
